@Justin we should work on a process describing how to do this. Can you take the lead on helping us write the doc. We can solicit feedback from Kerry, Hari and others on how to do this.

We can then turn this doc into a guide.

Let’s work on getting something ready by next week. @shaunak — how quickly do we need to turn around a doc like this?

Yup, in the longer run Test Runner seems to be the correct way to go.  In the short term, we might want to document a process for them.

If we can have a skeleton proposal with high level boxes by Monday EOD, that’d be great.  We can working on adding more details in the document as we go along.

